'''2021年俄罗斯反普京示威'''始于当年1月23日，[[俄羅斯|俄羅斯]]各地爆發反對執政超過20年[[弗拉基米尔·普京|弗拉基米爾·普京]]的示威。反对派领袖[[阿列克谢·纳瓦利内|阿列克谢·纳瓦利内]]遭逮捕、刻畫[[普京宮|普京宮]]内情的紀錄片《[[普京宫殿：史上最大的贿赂|普京宫殿：史上最大的贿赂]]》正式發行而觸發民憤皆是示威爆發的主因<ref name="tmt">{{cite web|url=https://www.themoscowtimes.com/2021/01/22/as-its-happening-russia-rallies-for-navalnys-release-a72705|title=As It's Happening: Russia Rallies for Navalny's Release|website=The Moscow Times|date=2021-01-23|accessdate=2021-01-27|archive-date=2021-01-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210124102130/https://www.themoscowtimes.com/2021/01/23/as-it-happened-tens-of-thousands-rally-for-navalnys-release-across-russia-a72705|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="novayagazeta">{{cite web|date=2021-01-23|title=Акции в поддержку Навального|url=https://novayagazeta.ru/articles/2021/01/23/88838-protesty-v-rossii-23-yanvarya-online|website=novayagezeta.ru|accessdate=2021-01-26|archive-date=2021-01-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210123210633/https://novayagazeta.ru/articles/2021/01/23/88838-protesty-v-rossii-23-yanvarya-online|dead-url=no}}</ref>。抗議活動第一天共波及俄罗斯198个城镇，是自[[2011年－2013年俄罗斯示威|2011年－2013年俄罗斯示威]]以來該國最大規模的反政府抗議事件<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.bbc.com/russian/live/news-55779010|title=День всероссийского протеста: как прошли акции в поддержку Навального|website=bbc.com|date=23 January 2021|access-date=2021-01-27|archive-date=2021-01-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210124101350/https://www.bbc.com/russian/live/news-55779010|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="tmt2">{{cite web|date=23 January 2021|title=Protests for Jailed Kremlin Critic Navalny Sweep Russia|url=https://www.themoscowtimes.com/2021/01/23/protests-for-jailed-kremlin-critic-navalny-sweep-russia-a72708|website=The Moscow Times|access-date=2021-01-27|archive-date=2021-01-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210124102133/https://www.themoscowtimes.com/2021/01/23/protests-for-jailed-kremlin-critic-navalny-sweep-russia-a72708|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://twitter.com/bbcrussian/status/1354757271356583937?s=21|title=Митинги в поддержку Алексей Навальный в России 23 января 2021 года|website=twitter.com|date=28 January 2021|access-date=2021-02-06|archive-date=2021-05-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210511001431/https://twitter.com/bbcrussian/status/1354757271356583937?s=21|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.theguardian.com/world/2021/jan/23/alexei-navalny-supporters-join-protests-across-russia|title=Tens of thousands protest in Russia calling for Navalny's release|website=The Guardian|date=23 January 2021|access-date=2021-01-26|archive-date=2021-01-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210129080707/https://www.theguardian.com/world/2021/jan/23/alexei-navalny-supporters-join-protests-across-russia|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2月2日，納瓦尼三年半的緩刑刑期被替換成徒刑，減去之前經受過的軟禁時期後，他仍要面臨爲期兩年半的監禁<ref name="tmt-2feb"/>。

2月4日，納瓦尼的幕僚長[[列昂尼德·沃爾科夫|列昂尼德·沃爾科夫]]表示直到春天或夏天前不會再舉行任何示威活動，以專注在秋季的[[2021年俄羅斯國家杜馬選舉|國家杜馬選舉]]。他也稱團隊將動用“外交方式”施壓政府釋放納瓦尼<ref name="meduza-suspended">{{cite web|url=https://meduza.io/en/news/2021/02/04/navalny-s-team-suspends-further-protests-until-the-spring-refocusing-on-campaign-efforts-ahead-of-russia-s-fall-parliamentary-elections|title=Navalny's team suspends further protests until the spring, refocusing on campaign efforts ahead of Russia's fall parliamentary elections|website=Meduza|date=4 February 2021|access-date=2021-08-13|archive-date=2021-10-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211029091155/https://meduza.io/en/news/2021/02/04/navalny-s-team-suspends-further-protests-until-the-spring-refocusing-on-campaign-efforts-ahead-of-russia-s-fall-parliamentary-elections|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="tmt-4feb">{{cite web|url=https://www.themoscowtimes.com/2021/02/04/navalnys-team-announces-no-more-protests-until-spring-a72839|title=Navalny’s Team Announces No More Protests Until Spring|website=The Moscow Times|date=4 February 2021|access-date=2021-02-09|archive-date=2021-05-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210511001451/https://www.themoscowtimes.com/2021/02/04/navalnys-team-announces-no-more-protests-until-spring-a72839|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 事件背景 ==
{{further|俄羅斯反對普京的聲音|阿列克谢·纳瓦利内中毒案}}

2020年8月20日，納瓦尼在一班自[[托木斯克|托木斯克]]飛往[[莫斯科|莫斯科]]的航班上遭人用[[神經性毒劑|神經性毒劑]][[阿列克谢·纳瓦利内中毒案|下毒]]，被緊急送院<ref name="bbc-2020">{{cite news|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-europe-53844958|title=Russian opposition leader Alexei Navalny 'poisoned'|work=BBC News|date=2020-08-20|access-date=2020-08-20|archive-date=2020-08-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200820094717/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-europe-53844958|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他隨後獲轉移至[[德國|德國]][[柏林|柏林]]接受治療，並在9月22日出院<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.themoscowtimes.com/2020/09/14/navalny-taken-off-ventilator-as-novichok-recovery-continues-german-hospital-a71437|title=Navalny Taken Off Ventilator as Novichok Recovery Continues – German Hospital|website=[[The_Moscow_Times|The Moscow Times]]|date=2020-09-14|accessdate=2021-01-26|archive-date=2020-10-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201009011924/https://www.themoscowtimes.com/2020/09/14/navalny-taken-off-ventilator-as-novichok-recovery-continues-german-hospital-a71437|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="reuters-02/09/20">{{cite news|last1=Zverev|first1=Anton|last2=Tétrault-Farber|first2=Gabrielle|last3=Ivanova|first3=Polina|last4=Teterevleva|first4=Anastasia|last5=Kiselyova|first5=Maria|date=2020-08-27|title=Russian prosecutors say no need for criminal investigation in Navalny affair|work=[[Reuters|Reuters]]|editor-last=Rao|editor-first=Sujata|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-russia-politics-navalny-probe/russian-prosecutors-say-no-need-for-criminal-investigation-in-navalny-affair-idUSKBN25N14R|access-date=2020-09-02|archive-date=2021-01-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210114103012/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-russia-politics-navalny-probe/russian-prosecutors-say-no-need-for-criminal-investigation-in-navalny-affair-idUSKBN25N14R|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|date=2020-09-09|title=Russia Protests Germany's 'Unfounded Accusations' In Navalny Poisoning Case|url=https://www.rferl.org/a/russia-protests-germany-s-unfounded-accusations-in-navalny-poisoning-case/30828886.html|access-date=2020-12-24|website=[[Radio_Free_Europe/Radio_Liberty|Radio Free Europe/Radio Liberty]]|archive-date=2021-01-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210114070218/https://www.rferl.org/a/russia-protests-germany-s-unfounded-accusations-in-navalny-poisoning-case/30828886.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[禁止化學武器組織|禁止化學武器組織]]（{{lang|en|OPCW}}）確認施襲者所使用的神經性毒劑為[[諾維喬克|諾維喬克]]<ref>{{Cite web|date=2020-10-06|title=Watchdog Says Novichok-Type Nerve Agent Found in Navalny Samples|url=https://www.themoscowtimes.com/2020/10/06/watchdog-says-novichok-type-nerve-agent-found-in-navalny-samples-a71674|website=The Moscow Times|accessdate=2021-01-26|archive-date=2021-01-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210118022812/https://www.themoscowtimes.com/2020/10/06/watchdog-says-novichok-type-nerve-agent-found-in-navalny-samples-a71674|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|date=2020-10-06|title=OPCW: Novichok found on Alexei Navalny samples|url=https://www.dw.com/en/opcw-novichok-found-on-alexei-navalny-samples/a-55176999|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201214061834/https://www.dw.com/en/opcw-novichok-found-on-alexei-navalny-samples/a-55176999|archive-date=2020-12-14|access-date=2020-10-06|website=[[Deutsche_Welle|Deutsche Welle]]}}</ref>。雖然[[俄羅斯政府|克里姆林宮]]否認涉及此宗下毒案<ref>{{Cite news|date=2020-08-25|title=Kremlin dismisses claims Putin poisoned Navalny|language=en-GB|work=BBC News|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-53903314|access-date=2020-08-25|archive-date=2021-01-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210114025422/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-53903314|dead-url=no}}</ref>，但[[歐盟|歐盟]]及[[英國|英國]]皆對該國采取了反制行動，宣佈制裁六名高級俄國官員及一家國有化學中心<ref>{{cite web|last=Chappell|first=Bill|date=2020-10-15|title=EU Sanctions Russian Officials Over Navalny Poisoning, Citing Chemical Weapons Use|url=https://www.npr.org/2020/10/15/923982672/eu-sanctions-russian-officials-over-navalny-poisoning-citing-chemical-weapons-us|access-date=2020-10-20|website=NPR.org|archive-date=2020-10-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201015180325/https://www.npr.org/2020/10/15/923982672/eu-sanctions-russian-officials-over-navalny-poisoning-citing-chemical-weapons-us|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|date=2020-10-15|title=Navalny Novichok poisoning: EU sanctions hit top Russians|work=BBC News|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-54552480|access-date=2020-10-20|archive-date=2021-01-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210117175444/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-54552480|dead-url=no}}</ref>。納瓦尼本身則指控[[俄羅斯總統|俄羅斯總統]][[弗拉基米尔·普京|普丁]]策劃了此次下毒案<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/amp/world-europe-54369664|title=Alexei Navalny blames Vladimir Putin for poisoning him|date=2020-10-01|last1=Rainsford|first1=Sarah|website=BBC News|accessdate=2021-01-26|archive-date=2020-10-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201003164809/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/amp/world-europe-54369664|dead-url=no}}</ref>，獨立調查網站“{{lang|en|{{le|Bellingcat|Bellingcat}}}}”及獨立媒體《{{lang|en|{{le|The Insider|The Insider (website)}}}}》發佈的調查報告稱俄羅斯[[聯邦安全局|聯邦安全局]]的特務對納瓦尼下毒<ref name="bbc-investigation">{{cite web|date=2020-12-14|title=Alexei Navalny: Report names 'Russian agents' in poisoning case|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-europe-55303703|website=[[BBC_News|BBC News]]|accessdate=2021-01-26|archive-date=2021-01-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210118063724/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-europe-55303703|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2021年1月17日，納瓦尼在一抵達俄羅斯後即刻遭[[俄羅斯警察|俄羅斯警察]]以違反緩刑爲由逮捕<ref name="arrest2021">{{cite web |url=https://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-55694598 |title=Russia Navalny: Poisoned opposition leader held after flying home |publisher=BBC News |date=2021-01-17 |access-date=2021-01-17 |language=en |archive-date=2021-01-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210121202407/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-55694598 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。{{le|俄羅斯聯邦監獄局|Federal Penitentiary Service}}（{{lang|en|FSIN}}）在納瓦尼抵俄前就已經指出他有可能因違反緩刑規定面對牢獄之災，且宣稱該局“有義務”拘押他<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.themoscowtimes.com/2021/01/14/russia-says-obliged-to-detain-navalny-upon-return-a72611|title=Russia Warns 'Obliged' to Detain Kremlin Critic Navalny on Return|website=The Moscow Times|date=2021-01-14|accessdate=2021-01-26|archive-date=2021-01-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210117224440/https://www.themoscowtimes.com/2021/01/14/russia-says-obliged-to-detain-navalny-upon-return-a72611|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2014年，納瓦尼因{{le|葉露芝案|Alexei Navalny#Yves Rocher case and home arrest}}被判緩刑，但他指判決是出於政治考量，而[[歐洲人權法院|歐洲人權法院]]則在2017年宣判納瓦尼的判刑不公<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.rferl.org/a/aleksei-oleg-navalny-yves-rocher-case-echr-unfairly-convicted/28799784.html|title=Human Rights Court Says Navalny Unfairly Convicted In 'Yves Rocher Case'|date=2017-10-17|website=rferl.org|accessdate=2021-01-26|archive-date=2021-01-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210120201333/https://www.rferl.org/a/aleksei-oleg-navalny-yves-rocher-case-echr-unfairly-convicted/28799784.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://meduza.io/en/news/2021/01/18/alexey-navalny-remanded-in-custody-for-30-days-pending-trial|title=Alexey Navalny remanded in custody for 30 days pending trial|website=Meduza.io|date=2021-01-18|accessdate=2021-01-26|archive-date=2021-01-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210118175448/https://meduza.io/en/news/2021/01/18/alexey-navalny-remanded-in-custody-for-30-days-pending-trial|dead-url=no}}</ref>。另一方面，[[俄羅斯聯邦偵查委員會|俄羅斯聯邦偵查委員會]]表示該會正對納瓦尼的詐欺指控作出調查<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.themoscowtimes.com/2021/01/17/kremlin-foe-navalny-flying-back-to-russia-despite-risk-of-arrest-a72633|title=Kremlin Foe Navalny Flying Back to Russia Despite Risk of Arrest|date=2020-01-17|website=The Moscow Times|accessdate=2021-01-26|archive-date=2021-01-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210123210633/https://www.themoscowtimes.com/2021/01/17/russia-detains-poisoned-kremlin-critic-navalny-on-return-to-home-soil-a72633|dead-url=no}}</ref>。納瓦尼遭逮捕隔日，法庭判定納瓦尼違反緩刑條例，須還押至2月15日。該局在納瓦尼遭羈押的警察局内設立了臨時法庭，而他將在1月29日面對另一項判決，法官將就納瓦尼的緩刑是否應替換成牢期作出審判<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-55700312|title=Alexei Navalny: Poisoned Putin critic Navalny jailed for 30 days|date=2021-01-18|website=bbc.com|publisher=[[BBC_News|BBC News]]|accessdate=2021-01-26|archive-date=2021-01-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210122042010/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-55700312|dead-url=no}}</ref>。納瓦尼炮轟整起事件“極度無法無天”，並呼籲支持者走上街頭，要他們“不要靜默。反抗。走上街頭——並非爲了我，而是爲了你自己” 。納瓦尼的盟友[[列昂尼德·沃爾科夫|列昂尼德·沃爾科夫]]表示他們為1月23日全國各地將舉行的示威做出了積極準備<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.themoscowtimes.com/2021/01/18/navalny-urges-russians-to-take-to-the-streets-over-jailing-a72646|title=Navalny Urges Russians To 'Take To The Streets' Over Jailing|website=The Moscow Times|date=2021-01-18|accessdate=2021-01-26|archive-date=2021-01-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210120221354/https://www.themoscowtimes.com/2021/01/18/navalny-urges-russians-to-take-to-the-streets-over-jailing-a72646|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

1月19日、納瓦尼仍在獄中時，他成立的[[反腐敗基金會|反腐敗基金會]]正式發行由納瓦尼配音的紀錄片《[[普京宫殿：史上最大的贿赂|普京宫殿：史上最大的贿赂]]》，指控普丁貪污，且呼籲民衆上街示威<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-europe-55732296|title=Alexei Navalny: Millions watch jailed critic's 'Putin palace' film|website=BBC News|date=2021-01-20|accessdate=2021-01-26|archive-date=2021-01-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210121175146/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-europe-55732296|dead-url=no}}</ref>。抗議事件爆發前，紀錄片在{{lang|en|[[Youtube|Youtube]]}}上的點閱率已經突破六千萬大關<ref>{{cite web|url=https://charter97.org/ru/news/2021/1/22/408602/|title=У видео Навального о «дворце Путина» уже более 60 миллионов просмотров|website=charter97.org|date=2021-01-22|accessdate=2021-01-26|archive-date=2021-01-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210124102130/https://charter97.org/ru/news/2021/1/22/408602/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。紀錄片發行隔日，{{le|俄羅斯聯邦通信、信息技術與大衆傳媒監督局|Federal Service for Supervision of Communications, Information Technology and Mass Media}}要求該國最受歡迎的社交網路服務網站{{lang|en|[[VKontakte|VKontakte]]}}（{{Lang|en|VK}}）及{{lang|en|[[TikTok|TikTok]]}}遏制號召民衆示威的訊息繼續傳播<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.interfax.ru/russia/746192|title=МВД пригрозило распространителям призывов протестовать 23 января|website=[[Interfax|Interfax]]|date=2021-01-21|accessdate=2021-01-26|archive-date=2021-01-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210121234516/https://www.interfax.ru/russia/746192|dead-url=no}}</ref>，然而此項要求是否收穫成效則備受質疑<ref name="auto">{{Cite web|url=https://gizmodo.com/russia-claims-tiktok-deleted-young-people-s-protest-pre-1846112989|title=Russian Government Claims TikTok Deleted Young People’s Protest Prep Videos at Its Behest|first=Aliide|last=Naylor|website=Gizmodo|accessdate=2021-01-24|archive-date=2021-01-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210123213314/https://gizmodo.com/russia-claims-tiktok-deleted-young-people-s-protest-pre-1846112989|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

1月21日，當局開始逮捕包括[[柳博夫·索波爾|柳博夫·索波爾]]在内的納瓦尼助理及盟友<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.dw.com/ru/kak-vlasti-rf-pytajutsja-ne-dopustit-akcij-v-podderzhku-navalnogo/a-56306691|title=Как власти России готовились к акциям в поддержку Навального|website=dw.com|date=2021-01-23|accessdate=2021-01-26|archive-date=2021-01-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210122011446/https://www.dw.com/ru/kak-vlasti-rf-pytajutsja-ne-dopustit-akcij-v-podderzhku-navalnogo/a-56306691|dead-url=no}}</ref>，其中有人遭判坐牢或罰款，而索波爾則獲釋放<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.themoscowtimes.com/2021/01/22/navalny-allies-jailed-fined-as-russia-vows-crackdown-on-protests-a72697|title=Navalny Allies Jailed, Fined as Russia Vows Protest Crackdown|website=The Moscow Times|date=2021-01-22|accessdate=2021-01-26|archive-date=2021-01-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210124102131/https://www.themoscowtimes.com/2021/01/22/navalny-allies-jailed-fined-as-russia-vows-crackdown-on-protests-a72697|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[俄羅斯聯邦内務部|俄羅斯聯邦内務部]]揚言起訴號召他人參與抗議的民衆，而{{le|俄羅斯聯邦檢察總長|Prosecutor-General of Russia|檢察總長}}則命令審察機構，即通信、信息技術與大衆傳媒監督局禁止網民訪問宣傳抗議活動的網站<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.themoscowtimes.com/2021/01/21/russia-threatens-arrests-prosecutions-for-promoting-navalny-protests-a72683|title=Russia Threatens Arrests, Prosecutions for Promoting Navalny Protests|website=The Moscow Times|date=2021-01-21|accessdate=2021-01-26|archive-date=2021-01-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210121234138/https://www.themoscowtimes.com/2021/01/21/russia-threatens-arrests-prosecutions-for-promoting-navalny-protests-a72683|dead-url=no}}</ref>。22日，内務部發佈文告警告民衆勿鼓動及參與抗議事件，聲明指嘗試舉辦未經許可的活動及“示威者的挑釁行爲”將被視爲“對公衆秩序的威脅”，且將“即刻遭鎮壓”<ref>{{cite web|url=https://77.xn--b1aew.xn--p1ai/news/item/22690368|title=ГУ МВД России по г. Москве предупреждает об ответственности за участие в несанкционированных акциях|website=77.мвд.рф|date=2021-01-22|accessdate=2021-01-26|archive-date=2021-01-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210124102133/https://77.xn--b1aew.xn--p1ai/news/item/22690368|dead-url=no}}</ref>。社交媒體開始移除關於抗議的消息，其中{{Lang|en|VK}}阻止用戶訪問多個抗議頁面，若嘗試點開頁面則能看到{{Lang|en|VK}}的聲明，稱他們應檢察官辦公室要求封鎖頁面<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.znak.com/2021-01-22/vkontakte_nachal_blokirovat_informaciyu_o_23_yanvarya|title=«ВКонтакте» начал блокировать информацию о 23 января|website=znak.com|date=2021-01-22|accessdate=2021-01-26|archive-date=2021-01-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210124102132/https://www.znak.com/2021-01-22/vkontakte_nachal_blokirovat_informaciyu_o_23_yanvarya|dead-url=no}}</ref>。通信、信息技術與大衆傳媒監督局也稱{{Lang|en|VK}}、{{Lang|en|[[Instagram|Instagram]]}}、{{Lang|en|Tiktok}}及{{Lang|en|Youtube}}已經阻止網民訪問特定内容，且表示這些頁面“呼籲兒童參與非法大型集會”<ref>{{cite web|url=https://rkn.gov.ru/news/rsoc/news73310.htm|title=Социальные сети удаляют призывы к детям участвовать в незаконных массовых акциях|website=rkn.gov.ru|date=2021-01-22|accessdate=2021-01-26|archive-date=2021-01-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210122142500/https://rkn.gov.ru/news/rsoc/news73310.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。然而，[[臉書|臉書]]及{{Lang|en|Youtube}}都對此作出否認。臉書指出他們“收到當地監管機構要求，限制用戶訪問宣揚抗議活動的内容，但因此類内容並無違反臉書的社群規範，將獲保留”<ref name="auto"/>。

==抗議活動==

=== 1月23日：示威爆发 ===
