[[路透社|路透社]]預測[[莫斯科|莫斯科]]約有40,000人參與抗議活動，然而有關當局預測僅有4,000人現身，其他機構預測的參與人數則從15,000至25,000不等<ref>{{cite web|date=2021-01-23|title=Police crack down on Russian protests against jailing of Kremlin foe Navalny|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/idUSKBN29R10S|website=Reuters|accessdate=2021-01-27|archive-date=2021-01-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210124102132/https://www.reuters.com/article/idUSKBN29R10S|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="bbc">{{cite web|date=2021-01-23|title=День всероссийского протеста: как проходят акции в поддержку Навального|url=https://www.bbc.com/russian/live/news-55779010|website=BBC Russian|accessdate=2021-01-27|archive-date=2021-01-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210124101350/https://www.bbc.com/russian/live/news-55779010|dead-url=no}}</ref>。抗議人士在[[特維爾大街|特維爾大街]]及[[普希金廣場|普希金廣場]]聚集，隊伍一直延伸到納瓦尼被扣的{{le|巴特罗斯卡亚蒂什纳监狱|Matrosskaya Tishina}}<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.znak.com/2021-01-23/dymovye_shashki_i_izbieniya_kak_v_moskve_proshel_miting_obyavlennyy_komandoy_navalnogo|title="Леха, выходи" – Дымовые шашки и избиения: как в Москве прошел митинг, объявленный командой Навального|website=Znak.com|date=2021-01-23|accessdate=2021-01-27|archive-date=2021-01-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210124102625/https://www.znak.com/2021-01-23/dymovye_shashki_i_izbieniya_kak_v_moskve_proshel_miting_obyavlennyy_komandoy_navalnogo|dead-url=no}}</ref>。防暴警察在抗議活動開始前就開始驅散及逮捕示威者<ref name="tmt"/>，納瓦尼之妻{{le|尤利婭·納瓦爾納亞|Yulia Navalnaya}}在[[莫斯科地鐵|莫斯科地鐵]][[剧院站_(莫斯科地铁)|劇院站]]出口被捕<ref>{{cite web|date=2021-01-23|title=Опубликовано видео задержания Юлии Навальной|url=https://news.ru/society/opublikovano-video-zaderzhaniya-yulii-navalnoj/|website=news.ru|accessdate=2021-01-27|archive-date=2021-01-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210124101928/https://news.ru/society/opublikovano-video-zaderzhaniya-yulii-navalnoj/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，三小時後獲釋<ref>{{cite web|date=2021-01-23|title=В Москве задержали Юлию Навальную. Ее отпустили спустя три часа|url=https://meduza.io/news/2021/01/23/v-moskve-zaderzhali-yuliyu-navalnuyu|website=Meduza.io|accessdate=2021-01-27|archive-date=2021-01-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210124102141/https://meduza.io/news/2021/01/23/v-moskve-zaderzhali-yuliyu-navalnuyu|dead-url=no}}</ref>；納瓦尼盟友[[柳博夫·索波爾|柳博夫·索波爾]]則在抵達普希金廣場不久後遭短暫拘捕，之後也被罰款<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.rbc.ru/rbcfreenews/600c96a79a79477f7ae40389|title=Любовь Соболь оштрафовали на 20 тыс. руб. за организацию акции 23 января|website=rbc.ru|date=2021-01-24|accessdate=2021-01-27|archive-date=2021-01-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210129120451/https://www.rbc.ru/rbcfreenews/600c96a79a79477f7ae40389|dead-url=no}}</ref>。警員與抗議人士爆發搏鬥<ref name="tmt"/>。示威者亦在{{le|茨維諾大道|Tsvetnoy Boulevard}}截停一輛[[聯邦安全局|聯邦安全局]]車輛並以雪球攻擊之，司機據報眼睛受傷<ref>{{Cite web|date=2021-01-23|title=На московском протесте закидали снежками машину с мигалками. Водителю выбили глаз|url=https://openmedia.io/news/n1/na-moskovskom-proteste-zakidali-snezhkami-mashinu-s-migalkami-voditelyu-yakoby-vybili-glaz/|access-date=2021-01-24|website=Открытые Медиа|language=ru-RU|archive-date=2021-01-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126153708/https://openmedia.io/news/n1/na-moskovskom-proteste-zakidali-snezhkami-mashinu-s-migalkami-voditelyu-yakoby-vybili-glaz/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。官方媒體報道約40名警員受傷，[[俄羅斯聯邦偵查委員會|俄羅斯聯邦偵查委員會]]則宣佈該會已經就警員所受的暴力事件展開調查<ref>{{cite web|date=2021-01-23|title=В Москве, по данным РИА Новости и ТАСС, на акции протеста пострадали около 40 силовиков. СК начал проверку|url=https://meduza.io/news/2021/01/23/ria-novosti-soobschilo-o-39-silovikah-postradavshih-na-aktsii-v-moskve-sk-nachal-proverku|website=Meduza.io|accessdate=2021-01-27|archive-date=2021-01-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210124102142/https://meduza.io/news/2021/01/23/ria-novosti-soobschilo-o-39-silovikah-postradavshih-na-aktsii-v-moskve-sk-nachal-proverku|dead-url=no}}</ref>。俄羅斯饒舌歌手{{lang|en|{{le|Noize MC|Noize MC}}}}、饒舌團體{{lang|en|{{le|Kasta|Kasta}}}}成員伏拉迪（{{lang|en|Vladi}}）、導演{{le|瓦西里·西加列夫|Vasily Sigarev}}、作家{{le|德米特里·贝科夫|Dmitry Bykov}}皆現身普希金廣場參與抗議<ref name="znak1">{{cite web|url=https://www.znak.com/2021-01-23/na_akcii_v_podderzhku_navalnogo_prishli_artisty_i_muzykanty|title=Максим Виторган пожаловался, что его детей выгнали из аптеки "под ОМОН"|website=znak.com|date=2021-01-23|accessdate=2021-01-27|archive-date=2021-01-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210123153037/https://www.znak.com/2021-01-23/na_akcii_v_podderzhku_navalnogo_prishli_artisty_i_muzykanty|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

