與納瓦尼同爲政黨[[未來俄羅斯|未來俄羅斯]]創始人的[[列昂尼德·沃爾科夫|列昂尼德·沃爾科夫]]表示該團隊計劃在1月31日組織更多抗議活動，並在之後的每個星期六或星期日都走上街頭，直至他們的訴求獲滿足爲止（此計劃與[[2020－2021年白俄羅斯示威|2020－2021年白俄羅斯示威]]相似）<ref>{{Cite web|last=Welle (www.dw.com)|first=Deutsche|title=Глава штабов Навального подтвердил намерение провести акции 31 января {{!}} DW {{!}} 25.01.2021|url=https://www.dw.com/ru/glava-shtabov-navalnogo-podtverdil-namerenie-provesti-akcii-31-janvarja/a-56336029|access-date=2021-01-26|website=DW.COM|language=ru-RU|archive-date=2021-05-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210511002457/https://www.dw.com/ru/glava-shtabov-navalnogo-podtverdil-namerenie-provesti-akcii-31-janvarja/a-56336029|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="tmt"/><ref>{{cite web|date=23 January 2021|title=Леонид Волков анонсировал новые акции протеста через неделю|url=https://meduza.io/news/2021/01/23/leonid-volkov-anonsiroval-novye-aktsii-protesta-cherez-nedelyu|website=Meduza.io|access-date=2021-02-05|archive-date=2021-01-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210124102200/https://meduza.io/news/2021/01/23/leonid-volkov-anonsiroval-novye-aktsii-protesta-cherez-nedelyu|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|date=26 January 2021|title=Team Navalny announces location of this weekend's protest in Moscow|url=https://meduza.io/en/news/2021/01/26/team-navalny-announces-location-of-this-weekend-s-protest-in-moscow|website=Meduza.io|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210127063303/https://meduza.io/en/news/2021/01/26/team-navalny-announces-location-of-this-weekend-s-protest-in-moscow|archive-date=27 January 2021|access-date=27 January 2021}}</ref>。沃爾科夫也稱下一場抗議活動將在坐落於[[盧比揚卡廣場|盧比揚卡廣場]]的[[聯邦安全局|聯邦安全局]]總部外及總統府行政機關所在地[[舊廣場|舊廣場]]舉行，選在此地舉行抗議是因爲聯邦安全局就是“下毒者”，而行政機關“是監禁納瓦尼與否的決策者”<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.themoscowtimes.com/2021/01/26/navalnys-team-plans-weekend-protests-outside-fsb-a72738|title=Navalny's Team Plans Weekend Protests Outside FSB|website=The Moscow Times|date=27 January 2021|access-date=2021-02-05|archive-date=2021-05-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210511004122/https://www.themoscowtimes.com/2021/01/26/navalnys-team-plans-weekend-protests-outside-fsb-a72738|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

截至1月25日，莫斯科一般管轄權法院（{{lang|en|courts of general jurisdiction}}）共接獲448宗行政違規案，其中441宗涉嫌違反{{le|俄羅斯聯邦行政犯罪法典|Code of the Russian Federation on Administrative Offenses}}第20.2條文（違反抗議規則），另有七宗涉嫌違反第19.3條文之一（未能遵守警察、軍人或官員的合法指令或要求）<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.znak.com/2021-01-25/po_itogam_mitinga_v_podderzhku_navalnogo_v_moskve_v_sudy_postupilo_448_del|title=По итогам митинга в поддержку Навального в Москве в суды поступило 448 дел|website=Znak.com|date=25 January 2021|access-date=2021-02-05|archive-date=2021-05-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210511004145/https://www.znak.com/2021-01-25/po_itogam_mitinga_v_podderzhku_navalnogo_v_moskve_v_sudy_postupilo_448_del|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

一名俄羅斯{{lang|en|TikTok}}網紅及其友人被指示威期間破壞一輛隸屬聯邦安全局的車輛，隨後遭到拘捕。網上廣傳的視頻可見示威者猛烈攻擊行經抗議地點的車輛，司機據報眼部嚴重蒙傷，被送院治療<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.themoscowtimes.com/2021/01/27/russian-tiktokers-detained-for-attacking-fsb-car-at-navalny-protests-a72745|title=Russian TikTokers Detained for Attacking FSB Car at Navalny Protests|website=The Moscow Times|date=26 January 2021|access-date=2021-02-05|archive-date=2021-05-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210511013705/https://www.themoscowtimes.com/2021/01/27/russian-tiktokers-detained-for-attacking-fsb-car-at-navalny-protests-a72745|dead-url=no}}</ref>。截至1月26日，[[俄羅斯聯邦偵查委員會|俄羅斯聯邦偵查委員會]]已經開檔調查20宗刑事案件，其中多數為對執法當局使用暴力<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.rbc.ru/politics/26/01/2021/60104b169a794711c5bb41cd|title=Следователи доложили Бастрыкину о 20 уголовных делах по акциям 23 января|website=rbc.ru|date=26 January 2021|access-date=2021-02-05|archive-date=2021-05-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210511004143/https://www.rbc.ru/politics/26/01/2021/60104b169a794711c5bb41cd|dead-url=no}}</ref>；1月28日，偵查委員會再以沃爾科夫“游説未成年人犯罪”爲由對其開展刑事調查<ref>{{cite web|url=https://novayagazeta.ru/news/2021/01/28/167455-protiv-leonida-volkova-vozbudili-ugolovnoe-delo-o-prizyvah-podrostkov-k-uchastiyu-v-protestnyh-aktsiyah|title=Против Леонида Волкова возбудили уголовное дело из-за "призывов" к подросткам участвовать в протестных акциях|website=Novaya Gazeta|date=28 January 2021|access-date=2021-02-05|archive-date=2021-05-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210503015842/https://novayagazeta.ru/news/2021/01/28/167455-protiv-leonida-volkova-vozbudili-ugolovnoe-delo-o-prizyvah-podrostkov-k-uchastiyu-v-protestnyh-aktsiyah|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

網上亦流傳一段婦女遭防暴警察狠踹之視頻，該婦女據報在情況惡化之後再度入院。抗議活動隔日她獲准出院，她表示該警察曾前往醫院探訪，她也已經接受對方的道歉，唯之後又稱如此做只是爲了“不想被關注”。[[聖彼得堡|聖彼得堡]]檢察署强調事件正獲調查，但[[國家杜馬|俄羅斯國家杜馬]]主席[[维亚切斯拉夫·沃洛金|维亚切斯拉夫·沃洛金]]選擇捍衛該警官，認爲他“遭阻礙辦公”<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.themoscowtimes.com/2021/01/27/protester-kicked-by-russian-police-re-hospitalized-a72753|title=Protester Kicked by Russian Police Re-Hospitalized|website=The Moscow Times|date=27 January 2021|access-date=2021-02-05|archive-date=2021-05-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210511002538/https://www.themoscowtimes.com/2021/01/27/protester-kicked-by-russian-police-re-hospitalized-a72753|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

納瓦尼團隊稱俄羅斯警方在抗議活動數天后、1月31日的抗議活動前搜查了納瓦尼的公寓，當時其胞弟奧列格·納瓦尼（{{lang|en|Oleg Navalny}}）在場，他隨後遭警方帶走<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://meduza.io/news/2021/01/27/olega-navalnogo-posle-obyska-zabrali-politseyskie|access-date=2021-01-27|website=meduza.io|title=Олега Навального после обыска забрали полицейские|language=ru|archive-date=2021-05-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210511002542/https://meduza.io/news/2021/01/27/olega-navalnogo-posle-obyska-zabrali-politseyskie|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[反腐敗基金會|反腐敗基金會]]亦稱官員對其總部、“納瓦尼在綫”（{{lang|en|Navalny Live}}）錄音室及納瓦尼新聞秘書兼助理{{le|基拉·亞爾米許|Kira Yarmysh}}和其私人醫生阿納斯塔西婭·瓦西里耶娃（{{lang|en|Anastasia Vasilyeva}}）兩人的寓所進行了搜索。基金會主席日丹諾夫（{{lang|en|Ivan Zhdanov}}）稱[[俄羅斯聯邦内務部|内務部]]是以{{le|俄羅斯聯邦刑事法典|Criminal Code of Russia}}第236條文、即違反衛生及流行病標準爲由展開搜查<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.themoscowtimes.com/2021/01/27/russian-police-search-navalnys-apartment-hq-aides-a72735|title=Russian Police Search Navalny's Apartment, HQ – Aides|website=The Moscow Times|date=27 January 2021|access-date=2021-02-05|archive-date=2021-05-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210527215846/https://www.themoscowtimes.com/2021/01/27/russian-police-search-navalnys-apartment-hq-aides-a72735|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

納瓦尼團隊位於[[下諾夫哥羅德|下諾夫哥羅德]]的協調員羅曼·齊古博夫（{{lang|en|Roman Tregubov}}）於1月28日被拘捕，隔日遭判坐牢五天。1月30日、即下一場抗議活動舉行前，網上突然流出一段齊古博夫的自白影片，他宣佈自己辭職並促請民衆勿參與第二天的抗議活動。然而，齊古博夫的律師認爲他受到威脅而被迫錄製視頻，並公開齊古博夫給地方檢察官與該市地方法官寫的親筆信。信中齊古博夫强調其律師不在場見證之下由他做出的“聲明、證詞或籲請”應當被視作是“處於嚴刑拷打、壓力及外部逼迫之下所爲”。偵察委員會早前公佈的數段視頻中，也可見涉嫌攻擊執法人員而遭拘捕的示威者表示自己“深感抱歉”、且“後悔”<ref>{{cite web|url=https://meduza.io/en/feature/2021/01/30/i-ask-you-not-to-believe|title='I ask you not to believe' After reporting threats to his lawyer, Navalny's jailed campaign coordinator in Nizhny Novgorod appears in a strange confession video|website=Meduza.io/en|date=31 January 2021|access-date=2021-02-06|archive-date=2021-05-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210511004147/https://meduza.io/en/feature/2021/01/30/i-ask-you-not-to-believe|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 1月31日 ===
[[File:Police_and_OMON_on_Rusakovskaya_street.jpg|thumb]]{{lang|en|Rusakovskaya}}街]]
抗議活動開始前，當局決定封鎖[[莫斯科|莫斯科]]市中心包括[[亞歷山大公園站|亞歷山大公園站]]、[[獵人商行站|獵人商行站]]、[[劇院站_(莫斯科地鐵)|劇院站]]、[[革命廣場站_(莫斯科地鐵)|革命廣場站]]、[[庫茲涅茨克橋站|庫茲涅茨克橋站]]、[[盧比揚卡站|盧比揚卡站]]與[[基塔城站|基塔城站]]在内的[[莫斯科地鐵|地鐵]]車站大廳，且在市中心實施行動管制、禁止商店及餐館營業<ref name="bbc-31jan">{{cite web|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-europe-55876033|title=Russia braces for latest Navalny protests|website=BBC News|date=2021-01-31|access-date=2021-02-06|archive-date=2021-05-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210527215733/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-europe-55876033|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="meduza-jan31">{{cite web|url=https://meduza.io/live/2021/01/31/aktsii-za-navalnogo-31-yanvarya|title=Акции за Навального 31 января|website=Meduza|date=2021-01-31|access-date=2021-02-06|archive-date=2021-05-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210511002646/https://meduza.io/live/2021/01/31/aktsii-za-navalnogo-31-yanvarya|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.znak.com/2021-01-31/meriya_moskvy_predupredila_o_zakrytii_centralnyh_stanciy_metro|title=Мэрия Москвы предупредила о закрытии центральных станций метро|website=znak.com|date=2021-01-31|access-date=2021-02-06|archive-date=2021-05-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210511002621/https://www.znak.com/2021-01-31/meriya_moskvy_predupredila_o_zakrytii_centralnyh_stanciy_metro|dead-url=no}}</ref>。位於[[盧比揚卡廣場|盧比揚卡廣場]]的[[聯邦安全局|聯邦安全局]]總部同樣遭警方以警戒綫封鎖，避免民衆靠近<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.znak.com/2021-01-31/v_moskve_pered_akciey_v_podderzhku_navalnogo_ocepili_zdanie_fsb_na_lubyanke|title=В Москве перед акцией в поддержку Навального оцепили здание ФСБ на Лубянке|website=znak.com|date=2021-01-31|access-date=2021-02-06|archive-date=2021-05-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210511002626/https://www.znak.com/2021-01-31/v_moskve_pered_akciey_v_podderzhku_navalnogo_ocepili_zdanie_fsb_na_lubyanke|dead-url=no}}</ref>。抗議活動主辦當局隨即將示威起點轉移至[[蘇哈列夫站|蘇哈列夫站]]與[[紅門站|紅門站]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.znak.com/2021-01-31/v_moskve_perenesli_mesto_nachala_shestviya_storonnikov_navalnogo|title=В Москве перенесли место начала шествия сторонников Навального|website=znak.com|date=2021-01-31|access-date=2021-02-06|archive-date=2021-05-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210511004153/https://www.znak.com/2021-01-31/v_moskve_perenesli_mesto_nachala_shestviya_storonnikov_navalnogo|dead-url=no}}</ref>，警方反擊，逮捕聚集在當處的抗議人士，再要求地鐵營運商關閉地鐵站入口及出口<ref>{{cite web|url=https://meduza.io/news/2021/01/31/politsiya-nachala-massovye-zaderzhaniya-u-metro-krasnye-vorota|title=Полиция начала массовые задержания у метро "Красные ворота" в Москве|website=Meduza.io|date=2021-01-31|access-date=2021-02-06|archive-date=2021-05-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210511002647/https://meduza.io/news/2021/01/31/politsiya-nachala-massovye-zaderzhaniya-u-metro-krasnye-vorota|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://meduza.io/news/2021/01/31/v-moskve-zakryli-stantsii-metro-krasnye-vorota-i-suharevskaya|title=В Москве закрыли станции метро "Красные ворота" и "Сухаревская"|website=Meduza.io|date=2021-01-31|access-date=2021-02-06|archive-date=2021-05-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210511014956/https://meduza.io/news/2021/01/31/v-moskve-zakryli-stantsii-metro-krasnye-vorota-i-suharevskaya|dead-url=no}}</ref>。主辦方再轉移陣地至[[共青團廣場|共青團廣場]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.znak.com/2021-01-31/volkov_snova_smenil_mesto_mitinga_v_moskve_teper_on_zovet_vseh_na_komsomolskuyu_plochad|title=Волков снова сменил место митинга в Москве — теперь он зовет всех на Комсомольскую площадь|website=znak.com|date=2021-01-31|access-date=2021-02-06|archive-date=2021-05-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210511004221/https://www.znak.com/2021-01-31/volkov_snova_smenil_mesto_mitinga_v_moskve_teper_on_zovet_vseh_na_komsomolskuyu_plochad|dead-url=no}}</ref>，[[紅村站|紅村站]]及[[索科利尼基站|索科利尼基站]]的入口、出口旋即被關閉<ref name="meduza-jan31"/>。抗議人士之後往納瓦尼遭押的{{le|巴特罗斯卡亚蒂什纳监狱|Matrosskaya Tishina}}行進<ref name="tmt-31jan">{{cite web|url=https://www.themoscowtimes.com/2021/01/31/as-its-happening-russians-stage-fresh-navalny-protests-a72784|title=As It's Happening: Russians Stage Fresh Navalny Protests|website=The Moscow Times|date=2021-01-31|access-date=2021-02-06|archive-date=2021-01-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210131120531/https://www.themoscowtimes.com/2021/01/31/as-its-happening-russians-stage-fresh-navalny-protests-a72784|dead-url=no}}</ref>。納瓦尼之妻{{le|尤利婭·納瓦爾納亞|Yulia Navalnaya}}因出席{{le|索科利尼基區|Sokolniki District}}的抗議活動繼1月23日之後再次遭到拘捕<ref>{{cite web|url=https://meduza.io/news/2021/01/31/v-moskve-zaderzhali-yuliyu-navalnuyu|title=В Москве задержали Юлию Навальную|website=Meduza|date=2021-01-31|access-date=2021-02-06|archive-date=2021-05-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210511002756/https://meduza.io/news/2021/01/31/v-moskve-zaderzhali-yuliyu-navalnuyu|dead-url=no}}</ref>，並在數小時後獲釋，但因違反抗議法規而正受調查<ref>{{cite web|url=https://meduza.io/news/2021/01/31/yuliya-navalnuyu-otpustili-iz-otdela-politsii-scherbinki|title=Юлию Навальную отпустили из отдела полиции Щербинки|website=Meduza.io|date=2021-01-31|access-date=2021-02-06|archive-date=2021-05-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210511002735/https://meduza.io/news/2021/01/31/yuliya-navalnuyu-otpustili-iz-otdela-politsii-scherbinki|dead-url=no}}</ref>。警方在巴特罗斯卡亚蒂什纳监狱外頭展開大規模逮捕行動及嘗試驅散示威者，示威者於是調頭返回共青團廣場<ref name="meduza-en-31jan"/><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.znak.com/2021-01-31/u_matrosskoy_tishiny_gde_derzhat_navalnogo_nachalis_massovye_zaderzhaniya|title=У "Матросской тишины", где держат Навального, начались массовые задержания|website=znak.com|date=2021-01-31|access-date=2021-02-06|archive-date=2021-05-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210511002807/https://www.znak.com/2021-01-31/u_matrosskoy_tishiny_gde_derzhat_navalnogo_nachalis_massovye_zaderzhaniya|dead-url=no}}</ref>，但警方其後封鎖{{lang|en|Olkhovskaya}}街，將示威者困住。反對派政治人物{{le|伊利亞·雅辛|Ilya Yashin}}遭警方扣留<ref name="meduza-en-31jan"/>。

在[[聖彼得堡|聖彼得堡]]，抗議活動主辦方因應執法當局關閉[[涅夫斯基大街|涅夫斯基大街]]而將集會移往少先隊廣場（{{lang|en|Pionerskaya Square}}）舉行<ref>{{cite web|url=https://theins.ru/obshestvo/238982|title=Митинги 31 января. Онлайн|website=theins.ru|date=2021-01-31|access-date=2021-02-06|archive-date=2021-06-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210605001526/https://theins.ru/obshestvo/238982|dead-url=no}}</ref>。抗議人士起先聚集在{{le|布萊恩史塔夫青年劇院|Bryantsev Youth Theatre}}附近<ref name="meduza-en-31jan"/>，隨後往[[乾草廣場|乾草廣場]]前進並與警方爆發衝突，警方使用[[催淚彈|催淚彈]]阻止示威者援救被捕的同伴<ref>{{cite web|url=https://meduza.io/news/2021/01/31/fontanka-v-sankt-peterburge-dlya-razgona-protestuyuschih-politsiya-primenila-elektroshokery-i-slezotochivyy-gaz|title="Фонтанка": в Санкт-Петербурге для разгона протестующих полиция применила слезоточивый газ|website=Meduza.io|date=2021-01-31|access-date=2021-02-06|archive-date=2021-05-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210511002855/https://meduza.io/news/2021/01/31/fontanka-v-sankt-peterburge-dlya-razgona-protestuyuschih-politsiya-primenila-elektroshokery-i-slezotochivyy-gaz|dead-url=no}}</ref>。亦有報導指警方使用[[電擊槍|電擊槍]]，且有一名警官拿出手槍並指向抗議人士<ref>{{cite web|url=https://meduza.io/news/2021/01/31/v-tsentre-sankt-peterburga-politseyskiy-napravil-tabelnyy-pistolet-na-protestuyuschih|title=В центре Санкт-Петербурга полицейский направил табельный пистолет на протестующих|website=Meduza.io|date=2021-01-31|access-date=2021-02-06|archive-date=2021-05-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210511002752/https://meduza.io/news/2021/01/31/v-tsentre-sankt-peterburga-politseyskiy-napravil-tabelnyy-pistolet-na-protestuyuschih|dead-url=no}}</ref>。執法當局驅散聚集在少先隊廣場的示威者後，示威者行經{{lang|en|Zagorodny}}大道往[[莫斯科大街_(聖彼得堡)|莫斯科大街]]邁進<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.znak.com/2021-01-31/v_peterburge_obyavleno_ob_okonchanii_mitinga_shestviya_no_lyudey_prodolzhayut_zaderzhivat|title=В Петербурге объявлено об окончании митинга-шествия, но людей продолжают задерживать|website=znak.com|date=2021-01-31|access-date=2021-02-06|archive-date=2021-05-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210511004234/https://www.znak.com/2021-01-31/v_peterburge_obyavleno_ob_okonchanii_mitinga_shestviya_no_lyudey_prodolzhayut_zaderzhivat|dead-url=no}}</ref>，再移動至{{le|聖彼得堡立法議會|Legislative Assembly of Saint Petersburg}}建築物外頭，並在該處與警方衝突、遭强行驅散。示威者於是再返回布萊恩史塔夫青年劇院附近，主辦方宣佈集會結束，而聚集人士則遭警方驅散<ref name="meduza-en-31jan"/>。饒舌歌手{{lang|en|[[Oxxxymiron|Oxxxymiron]]}}在生日當天現身支持抗議活動並遭警方逮捕<ref>{{cite web|url=https://theins.ru/news/238989|title=Рэпера Оксимирона задержали на акции протеста в Петербурге|website=theins.ru|date=2021-01-31|access-date=2021-02-06|archive-date=2021-05-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210514171300/https://theins.ru/news/238989|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.znak.com/2021-01-31/reper_oxxxymiron_zaderzhan_na_akcii_v_podderzhku_navalnogo_v_moskve|title=Рэпер Oxxxymiron задержан на акции в поддержку Навального в Москве|website=znak.com|date=2021-01-31|access-date=2021-02-06|archive-date=2021-05-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210511002901/https://www.znak.com/2021-01-31/reper_oxxxymiron_zaderzhan_na_akcii_v_podderzhku_navalnogo_v_moskve|dead-url=no}}</ref>，隨後獲釋<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.znak.com/2021-01-31/oxxxymiron_otpuchen_iz_policii_posle_zaderzhaniya_na_mitinge_v_sankt_peterburge|title=Oxxxymiron отпущен из полиции после задержания на митинге в Санкт-Петербурге|website=znak.com|date=2021-01-31|access-date=2021-02-06|archive-date=2021-05-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210511002942/https://www.znak.com/2021-01-31/oxxxymiron_otpuchen_iz_policii_posle_zaderzhaniya_na_mitinge_v_sankt_peterburge|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

