hhiy-vytesnili-s-ploshhadi-minina-i-pozharskogo-id331488|access-date=2021-01-31|website=В городе N|language=ru|archive-date=2021-05-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210511004235/https://www.vgoroden.ru/novosti/protestuyushhiy-vytesnili-s-ploshhadi-minina-i-pozharskogo-id331488|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

